description:
CPollo is a decentralized platform that will allow the community the ability
to easily do their homework on ICO's, audit their token contracts ( we will most likely provide pre-audited templates ), track the ICOs us of the funds, freeze and retrieve some of their funds if it is determined by the community that there is a legitimate threat of being swindled by the ICO in question. This will provide the longevity and the prolonged freedom to the decentralized revolution which it so desperately needs.
name: Cpollo
